{"tid":1343430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗中環都要即散 事以至此 保命要緊 聽日先係重頭戲","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T19:08:26.000Z","uid":123562,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a1176cdba00d507db1b83368097b2e78d07a44c6","tid":1343430,"uid":123562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:45:50.000Z","msg":"老實講 過咗今晚 已經歸曬邊 唔需要再理民意 而係諗要點行動 大家集中討論同推行唔同方案，最好係又有影嚮力又合法嘅，等一家大細都可以參與，例如：<br />\n<br />\n1。三罷<br />\n2。花式入閘，個個都咁做啲大媽阿叔又會跟住做<br />\n3。遊唔同車河<br />\n<br />\n文宣方面都係以國外為主。以警方開鎗，警黑合作，建制黑社會勾結作重心。可以幫手send信同證據去所有國外機構同媒體，唔洗長篇大論唔洗再R template唔洗人地開post餵，見到就send, 人多佢自然會去睇去了解去調查。 國內主打黑社會同建制合作，打甩啲中間派嘅票。暫時諗到咁多，大家可再作學術討論。"},{"pid":"a6fb6d159c5a1a0e541dfb64116856fb713e412b","tid":1343430,"uid":123562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:51:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6d6a835381f953d359c76ba18cab64d8e9b5e4","tid":1343430,"uid":123562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:52:20.000Z","msg":"天佑香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dfd2d9b06032b7c004c575bbc49f45de808a63","tid":1343430,"uid":123562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:53:39.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a29d1e6c466ce98649f5e74aeb19f70d5a343c","tid":1343430,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:53:47.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n聽日輿論同文宣就係我哋戰場<br />\n=====================================<br />\n「文宣」聽日主題集火黑警連開三十多槍轟爆示威者頭，［撐警］何君堯指使元朗黑社會濫害平民！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1342705\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1342705</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/iDmdy6F.png\" data-thumbnai